DBMS :- 
-----------

 => Database Management System
 => DBMS is a software used to work with database.
 => using DBMS software we can create,read,update,delete data in db
 => DBMS is an interface between user and database.
 
    USER------------------DBMS--------------------DB

Types of DBMS  (Evolution of DBMS) :-
